## Province [/countries/:id/provinces/subid?include=includes]
Get a single Province object 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Country to perform action with. Has example value.
    + subid (required, number, `2`) ... Numeric `subid` of the Province to perform action with. Has example value.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `cities`, or `all`

### Retrieve a specific Province under a Country [GET]
